{"tid":2145871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[外國手足] 共產黨搵戲子讀稿拍抖音 詆毀外國人 宣揚仇外主義","createTime":"2020-08-08T09:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T10:23:05.000Z","uid":63830,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4c132af626b41acb815291867575ec852595b3fa","tid":2145871,"uid":63830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:04:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZLg5JNA-TIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZLg5JNA-TIs&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=e3bee911\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZLg5JNA-TIs</a><br />\n<br />\n美國YouTuber laowhy86近日於抖音發現大量內容相近影片，主要講述片主遇到外國人大聲交談/亂拋垃圾。片主上前制止，反被對方要求講英文。然後片主以支那口音呼籲對方遵守秩序，並勸喻對方學中文。外國人深受感動，更指片主英文流利，詢問片主是否美國人。<br />\n<br />\nlaowhy86原為於中国生活嘅美國人，後來因與朋友前往中国西北拍YouTube紀錄片，觸及共產黨紅線被通緝。幸及時逃離中国，其友於2018年起遭監禁至今。<br />\n<br />\nlaowhy86亦有拍片講解Tik Tok禁令，內容提及共產黨對企業有控制權，亦提及中国並無法治，美國人於Tik Tok內資料岌岌可危。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=La6yrMgkwiY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLa6yrMgkwiY&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=26195f3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=La6yrMgkwiY</a>"},{"pid":"9f02e9fdf60c435b8468fbb45c682aab5d7ef5bd","tid":2145871,"uid":63830,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:05:07.000Z","msg":"其實連登之前已經有post，不過似乎唔太貼題，所以我開多次。<br />\n<br />\n中國終於反制!!!  潮文新玩法: 美國佬去Starbucks正仆街<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144894\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2144894</a>"},{"pid":"dbec0067eab699d96d8b197635643563c7735e4b","tid":2145871,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:25:58.000Z","msg":"支那要多啲義和團<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034917b9112663096a38ec0c40ff59055024437c","tid":2145871,"uid":118330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci